# 作用：确认接口服务已经启动
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

# 作用：健康检查
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
Accept: application/json

###

# 作用：检索知识库中的相关切片
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/retrieval/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "如何重置密码？",
  "top_k": 3
}

###

# 作用：执行完整问答流程
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/answering/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "如何重置密码？",
  "top_k": 3
}

###

# 作用：导入单个本地文件
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/ingestion/file
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "E:/develop/py/project/support-copilot/resources/demo.md"
}
